{"id":4984,"date":"2024-01-22T05:01:30","date_gmt":"2020-01-21T23:31:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=4984"},"modified":"2023-05-25T16:40:05","modified_gmt":"2023-05-25T11:10:05","slug":"living-room-showcase-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-showcase-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"Put On A Show: Style Your Living Room With These Showcase Designs"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Show off those souvenirs and books with these showcase designs. Pick one that makes the most aesthetic sense to you.<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Introduction: <\/strong>The living room is the face of your home. The impression matters. Your living room must represent your personality and tastes. In this context, showcases can make your living room landscape stand out. They are not only used to displaying your curios, books or travel souvenirs but also keep your living room clutter-free by placing your favourite items within close reach.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Before buying or building a showcase consider the following:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Room Measurements<\/li><li>The Shape Of The Showcase<\/li><li>Budget<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\u2019s get started on the best options available when it comes to selecting showcase designs for your living room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contemporary Glass Showcase Design for living room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This white contemporary showcase design has a mix of open shelves, glass-panelled shelves and closed cabinets to hold everything you want to display together. It gives a neat look to your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/living-room-design\/\">living room interiors<\/a>. You can stack your favourite books under the TV, those prized possessions on the glass-panelled shelf and other decorative items on the TV shelf itself. This white-coloured showcase makes this room look more spacious, bright and fresh. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003239\/showcase-designs-for-living-room-with-glass.jpg\" alt=\"Glass showcase designs for living room that has open and glass panelled shelves\" class=\"wp-image-4987\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003239\/showcase-designs-for-living-room-with-glass.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003239\/showcase-designs-for-living-room-with-glass-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003239\/showcase-designs-for-living-room-with-glass-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003239\/showcase-designs-for-living-room-with-glass-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Showcase Design For Living Room That Doubles Up As A Partition<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sunmica-design\/\">wood-finished sunmica<\/a> showcase design is extremely suitable for homes with an open-style plan. Its unique setup and bold pillar-like panelling on opposite sides of each shelf provide the structure with adequate support and simultaneously acts as a divider between two rooms giving you required privacy too.  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003242\/corner-showcase-designs-for-drawing-room.jpg\" alt=\"Living room showcase design that doubles up as partition\" class=\"wp-image-4988\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003242\/corner-showcase-designs-for-drawing-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003242\/corner-showcase-designs-for-drawing-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003242\/corner-showcase-designs-for-drawing-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003242\/corner-showcase-designs-for-drawing-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Drawing Room Showcase With Glass<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This ornate glass showcase is a great choice for those who are looking to give their living room a classy makeover. Intricate carvings all around, pair of drawers beneath and multiple glass shelves speaks of elegance and royalty. Pair this showcase design with a white sideboard to complete the look with maximum impact.  <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003244\/living-room-showcase-with-glass.jpg\" alt=\"Living room showcase with glass which is a great choice for a classy makeover\" class=\"wp-image-4989\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003244\/living-room-showcase-with-glass.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003244\/living-room-showcase-with-glass-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003244\/living-room-showcase-with-glass-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003244\/living-room-showcase-with-glass-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hexagon-Shaped Wooden Wall Showcase Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another funky idea for your living room is this hexagon-shaped wall showcase design. It\u2019s breathtaking and sets your home apart from others with its five-frames built together in sequence. The shape provides sufficient stability. You can place both small and large artefacts with ease on shelves. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003246\/showcase-designs-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Wooden wall showcase designs for living room in hexagon shape\" class=\"wp-image-4990\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003246\/showcase-designs-for-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003246\/showcase-designs-for-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003246\/showcase-designs-for-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003246\/showcase-designs-for-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do you want a living room that is lively and livable\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02171514\/living-room-lively-livable.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Showcase For All Your Entertainment Needs<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This latest entertainment showcase design is just what you need to get the party started. It is utilitarian in nature and looks fabulous too. You can place your stereo, CD player, Wi-Fi, portable speakers, and related accessories for a social atmosphere right at home. The closed cabinet area is compact and stores wires and cables well. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003249\/cement-showcase-designs-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Entertainment showcase designs for living room to get the party started\" class=\"wp-image-4991\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003249\/cement-showcase-designs-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003249\/cement-showcase-designs-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003249\/cement-showcase-designs-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003249\/cement-showcase-designs-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">L-Shaped TV Showcase Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Here is an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/l-shape-tv-unit-design-ideas\/\">L-shaped TV<\/a> showcase design that is chic and compact.\u00a0 It does not take up the entire space on your wall. This vertically aligned showcase design is where you can stack your favourite books and other items. It looks cool and is a perfect blend of modernity and style. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003252\/showcase-design-for-drawing-room.jpg\" alt=\"L-shaped TV showcase design that is chic and compact\" class=\"wp-image-4992\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003252\/showcase-design-for-drawing-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003252\/showcase-design-for-drawing-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003252\/showcase-design-for-drawing-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003252\/showcase-design-for-drawing-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Designer Corner&nbsp; Living Room Wooden Showcase Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Looking for a showcase that fills those unused corner spaces? Try out this designer zig-zag showcase design. Its minimalistic build blends perfectly well with your living room landscape, adding a touch of sophistication to space. Pair it with <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/10-best-sturdy-furnitutre-woods\/\">wood-textured furniture<\/a> and modern wall frames and you are good to go. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003255\/designer-showcase-design-for-your-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Living room wooden showcase design that creates a designer corner in your house\" class=\"wp-image-4993\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003255\/designer-showcase-design-for-your-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003255\/designer-showcase-design-for-your-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003255\/designer-showcase-design-for-your-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003255\/designer-showcase-design-for-your-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"https:\/\/api.whatsapp.com\/send?phone=916366910437&text=Hello%20Design%20Cafe%20Team,%20I%20am%20interested%20to%20know%20more%20about%20your%20home%20interior%20design%20services\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Do y