edia.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003300\/sleek-showcase-ideas-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Sleek living room showcase design for a cohesive and stylish look\" class=\"wp-image-4995\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003300\/sleek-showcase-ideas-for-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003300\/sleek-showcase-ideas-for-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003300\/sleek-showcase-ideas-for-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003300\/sleek-showcase-ideas-for-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Lift Up Tv Showcase Design For Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This showcase design is ideal for small homes that thrive on multifunctionality and aesthetics. A lift-up shutter gives this showcase a seamless look on the outside and lets you hide all those ugly wires and cables behind. Behind it, you will find shelves for extra storage.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003302\/living-room-showcase-outside-for-living-room-showcase-items.jpg\" alt=\"Lift up TV Living room showcase design which is ideal for small homes\" class=\"wp-image-4996\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003302\/living-room-showcase-outside-for-living-room-showcase-items.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003302\/living-room-showcase-outside-for-living-room-showcase-items-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003302\/living-room-showcase-outside-for-living-room-showcase-items-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003302\/living-room-showcase-outside-for-living-room-showcase-items-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Wall-Mounted Showcase With Shelves<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Are you looking for something elemental? Then this wall-mounted showcase with shelves is just the right one for you. It has five shelves of varying lengths mounted horizontally on the wall. This design is easy to manage as it provides extra floor space, often a problem for small homes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003305\/wooden-showcase-designs-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Wall mounted living room showcase designs with shelves to provide extra floor space\" class=\"wp-image-4997\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003305\/wooden-showcase-designs-for-living-room.jpg 800w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003305\/wooden-showcase-designs-for-living-room-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003305\/wooden-showcase-designs-for-living-room-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/01\/21003305\/wooden-showcase-designs-for-living-room-150x100.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Since your living room is your personal comfort lounge, you must rethink your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">home interiors<\/a> with the most visually appealing showcase design. Sprinkle some sophistication into your home interiors. So, select a showcase design that represents you in the most unique way and watch your living room come alive!<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Dreamy Interiors That Spell 'WOW'<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our design experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06164015\/91.png\"\n                    selected>\n                    +91\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+44\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/